34 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
35 recognize and commend Bethann Frillman for her exceptional career and dedicated service
36 to DeKalb County as well as extend the most sincere best wishes for continued health and
37 happiness.
38 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
39 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Bethann Frillman.
